USA. These reports represent both suspected and probable cases according
to the WHO case definitions <http://www.who.int/csr/sars/casedefinition/en/>.
It would be of interest to know the breakdown of cases by category
(suspected vs probable according to the WHO case definitions), the
descriptive epidemiology of the cases, as well as their probable source of
infection (travel related, contact with known case, nosocomial contact). -
